### API Test Examples - Postman/cURL

## 1. Read Account (Success)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/1001234567

Expected: 200 OK with account details

---

## 2. Read Account (Not Found)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/9999999999

Expected: 404 NOT_FOUND

---

## 3. Deposit Transaction
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/1001234567/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionType": "DEPOSIT",
  "amount": 5000.00
}

Expected: 200 OK, balance increases from $15,250.75 to $20,250.75

---

## 4. Withdrawal Transaction
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/1001234570/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionType": "WITHDRAWAL",
  "amount": 2000.00
}

Expected: 200 OK, balance decreases from $8,750.50 to $6,750.50

---

## 5. Insufficient Funds
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/1001234578/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionType": "WITHDRAWAL",
  "amount": 15000.00
}

Expected: 400 BAD_REQUEST (available balance: $9,850.25)

---

## 6. Balance Adjustment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/1001234580/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionType": "ADJUSTMENT",
  "amount": 15000.00
}

Expected: 200 OK, balance set to $15,000.00

---

## 7. Validation Error (Negative Amount)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/1001234567/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionType": "DEPOSIT",
  "amount": -1000.00
}

Expected: 400 BAD_REQUEST with validation error

---

## 8. Validation Error (Missing Fields)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/1001234567/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionType": "DEPOSIT"
}

Expected: 400 BAD_REQUEST (amount is required)

---

## 9. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

Expected: 200 OK with status UP

---

## 10. API Documentation
GET http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html

Opens interactive Swagger UI for testing all endpoints
